result.name: 深記海南粉

reviews.text:
Interesting Hainan Style mixed noodles.

It's not in a soup but kind of wet mixed with ingredients:  peanuts, red and green onions, cilantro, pickled cabbage, peppered pork, crunchy wonton skins, bamboo shoots, bean sprouts,rice noodles.. and lots of raw chopped garlic!
Then you use the Yellow Hainan hot sauce (habenero?) on the table top and mixed together.
Its unique and quite delicious.
All for $35.
They are also famous for Hainan chicken rice of course.
勁難食 骨多過肉 是但搵d頭尾砌埋一碟俾你就算 飯冇油香味 店鋪衛生環境好惡劣下 傻仔先去食
海南雞油飯好食,可以揀雞脾,不另加錢。
海南雞飯套餐48元，豬雜飯38元，價加得快左d.   But delicious!  送胡椒湯，唔錯
同老豆來過吃，元朗鋪頭D野大部分都OK！
